From the table list, select a table and click on Forms

Click on the New form option and give the form a name
When the form preview is created you can hide the default name and owner columns if desired by clicking on the field and selecting hide in the menu 

Click on Add field in the menu to add fields to the form 

Clicking on the field name will add it to the next available row on the form 

Click on the General tab and then on the General option on the right hand side to change the column widths and other section details. 

Save and publish the form using the option top right. 
